reviews.review_text: Great show | Sound unbearable Background music to call this background music is a reach.
I WAS AT THIS SHOW Great show but this audio version is inferior--check out the other complete audio of this concert, much better overall sound.

These reviews below are STUPID This is a fantastic sounding audience recording for the era. Crank this up and be surprised. You know these burnouts below prob did a 15 second sound check on this in their cubicle at their temp job.

Skip this show at your PERIL!

Spectacular 1972 Tape The Truckin>Other One> Half Step is hotter than a charcoal grill. 

Amazing stuff. And an exquisite audience recording from 1972 no less. 

I consider myself a semi-audiophile and went digital Dead (with PCM and DAT) 25 years ago. So I can be pretty picky. But this stuff is highly recommended.
